{"tid":2101461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毓民踢爆黎智英老屈岑建勳恐嚇劉細良夫婦","createTime":"2020-07-09T22:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T01:48:31.000Z","uid":157483,"like":18,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"83cb5cedae9958b9c0939ce65e991a202b03f983","tid":2101461,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T22:34:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rOOygnajMAk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrOOygnajMAk&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=763f973e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rOOygnajMAk</a><br />\n<br />\n黎智英: 我離開香港, 就會中左「中共」既計. 「獅子頭」係中共臥底.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2095538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2095538</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個post成班信黎智英信到十足既傻仔入黎講下啦<br />\n成篇野名又唔敢開 閃閃縮縮又獅子頭又網紅夫婦 全部都係戴哂頭盔又死無對證既指控，根本疑點重重，砌人生豬肉味濃<br />\n劉細良黎智英都唔撚係第一次屈人嫁啦，唔撚記得田蕊妮啦？唔記得當年本民青點樣比黎智英抹黑？<br />\n好心啦 點解經歷左2019 到今時今日連登民智仲咁低，泛民大台講一句 完全唔fc唔求證下就信到十足？<br />\n唔撚怪得民主黨公民黨仲可以風光到今時今日"},{"pid":"d73739841ab7653f4878807ba56540884d5b1aad","tid":2101461,"uid":335434,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T22:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmYFNF9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmYFNF9.jpg&h=8bb3291e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/hk01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2Fhk01.jpg&h=ec21c36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岑建勳只不過係HK01嘅社長 肥佬黎肯定係亂捉鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28972dbc2d65a8d38ff4b958d7bb11e07c24feb","tid":2101461,"uid":157483,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"d73739841ab7653f4878807ba56540884d5b1aad","tid":2101461,"uid":335434,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T22:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht